s-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2)<span class="s1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll transparent;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>PSU: You have to prepare your own the ATX PSU. The S3 ships without a PSU. There are 4 PCI-e connectors for +12V DC input, but it only needs to connect two of them if without overclocking (PSU not included). Don’t parallel connected different DC input from different PSU into the same Hashing board.</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Features:</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Stand alone: The S3 mines stand alone, needs no proxy server.</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Quiet: The customized heat sinks mounted to the hash boards, one box over S3 to control the air flow, two fans mounted on both front and back ends that mean fans are able to work at lower speed to dissipate all heat easily. This design let S3 run at much lower noise level.</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Stable: Running 24 hours a day with minimal downtime.</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Accurate:<span class="s2" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll transparent;">&nbsp;</span>Hardware Error got from the sample unit rate is as low as 0.01%, hundreds times better than some competing products.</p><p class="p1" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: invert none 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Efficient: High energy efficiency to save your investment on PSU and electricity bills.</p>')
