</p></div></blockquote><div style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;"><div><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><font size="6">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</font></span></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p></div><blockquote style="text-align: start; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><blockquote style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div style="text-align: center;"><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">What is a CEX.IO voucher and what is it used for?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">It is a 192 bit, hex encoded, digital certificate entitling you to a share of the pool''s mining power. Once you have redeemed the certificate at CEX.IO your mining account will be credited the corresponding hashing power and you will start mining bitcoins and other coins instantly. For more information please go to CEX.IO website.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">How does the voucher look like?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">cc9f28dcaaf791232c5ae4149b34fcdcb787e4d455e7f799</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">This is just a specimen. Please don''t try to redeem it at CEX.IO</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">What is a digital certificate?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">A digital certificate is a very big number created via a random process and encoded according to one of the usually acceptable encoding schemes. CEX.IO uses 192bit long - hex encoded keys as certificates.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">What are cryptocurrencies?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Digital currency in which encryption techniques are used to regulate the generation of units of currency and verify the transfer of funds, operating independently of a central bank.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">What is bitcoin mining?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Mining is the process of adding transaction records to Bitcoin''s public ledger of past transactions. This ledger of past transactions is called the block chain as it is a chain of blocks. The block chain serves to confirm transactions to the rest of the network as having taken place.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">What is cloud mining?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Cloud Mining is the process of mining cryptocurrencies utilizing a remote datacenter with shared processing power often contracted through a Cloud Mining company. This type of mining allows users to mine cryptocurrency without having to manage their own hardware.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">What cryptocurrencies does CEX.IO cloud mine?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">At the moment they mine bitcoins, namecoins, IDX and DVC</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">How much cryptocurrencies will I mine with this voucher?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Mining cryptocurrencies is a competitive process. The amount of cryptocurrency you will receive depends on how successful the CEX.IO pool is overall. Please check their website for more details.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Can I stop mining and recover my investment?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">At the moment of writing CEX.IO offers the possibility to exchange your mining shares for either cryptocurrencies or fiat money. You can also withdraw your shares in the form of a new voucher. Please check CEX.IO website for the latest information on this respect.</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><font size="6">&nbsp;</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Will you deliver the voucher electronically?</font></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in;"></p><p lang="en-GB" style="text-align: left; margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri;"><font size="6">Probably not. We may agree to do so at our own discretion taking into consideration the value of the voucher, the feedback of the buyer and any previous successful transactions the buyer may have conducted with us. The fact that we delivered electronically a lower value voucher does not imply we will also deliver electronically a higher value voucher.</font></p></div></blockquote></blockquote></div></div>')
